thread.title: Ruth
thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Ruth

author: Ruth
title: Ruth
text: I was very pleased with the color and quality of the finish on the wooden frame. Since I ordered plexiglass and two mats, I did not have to assemble the corners myself (hooray!). The mats were well cut and the plexi dust free. All well packaged. I was short 4 screws, but they sent some within a few days when I reported the problem.
